original_title: Rhys Nicholson - Live at The Eternity Playhouse
overview: Award winning Rhys Nicholson performs his breakout 2016 show "Bona Fide" at Sydney's Eternity Theatre. Covering vast topics from flexitarians, to anxiety, to how to act at weddings.
title: Rhys Nicholson - Live at The Eternity Playhouse
